high_descs: Turn and go to the trash can.
Pick up the pen that is in the trash can.
Turn and go to the taller black dresser with the pen in hand.
Place the pen on top of the black dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move the pen to the dresser.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the end of the dresser and turn left at the wall to face the purple container on the floor.
Pick up the white pen from inside the purple container on the floor.
Turn left, hang a right around the dresser and turn left by the window to face the wooden shelf on a desk.
Put the pen in front of the blue credit card on the left side of the shelf on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a pen on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the small trash can.
Pick up the pen from inside the trash can.
Walk around the dresser to the taller dresser.
Put the pen down on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move the pen from the trash can to the tall dresser.
